'''乔治·伊恩·博伊德'''（{{lang-en|'''George Ian Boyd'''}}，{{bd|1985年|10月2日|catidx=Boyd, George}}）出生於[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[肯特郡|肯特郡]]的[[查塔姆|查塔姆]]，是一名[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場#翼鋒|左翼]]，出身[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]青訓系統，其後轉投仍在非聯賽的[[保罗夫史提芬足球俱乐部|史提芬納治]]，成名於[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]，現時效力[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球隊[[沙福特城足球會|沙福特城]]。

博伊德被[[保罗夫史提芬足球俱乐部|史提芬納治]]的球迷暱稱為「白[[比利|比利]]」（''White Pelé''）<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/premierleague/tottenham/6930616/Tottenham-manager-Harry-Redknapp-considering-move-for-Peterborough-duo.html |title=Tottenham manager Harry Redknapp considering move for Peterborough duo |publisher=''telegraph.co.uk'' |date=2010-01-04 |accessdate=2010-02-25 |archive-date=2010-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100108015149/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/premierleague/tottenham/6930616/Tottenham-manager-Harry-Redknapp-considering-move-for-Peterborough-duo.html }}</ref>，他這個綽號在轉投彼德堡後仍然在新球會中被球迷採納。

== 生平 ==
=== 球會 ===
博伊德早年在居住的[[梅德韋郡|梅德韋郡]]（Medway）踢球，最初為布雷霍斯特男童隊（Bredhurst Boys）比賽，其後加入肯特郡聯賽（Kent League）的{{le|Chatham Town F.C.||查塔姆鎮}}。博伊德與其任職[[的士|的士]][[司機|司機]]的父親同為[[水晶宫足球俱乐部|水晶宮]]的支持者，但他卻加入其鄰會的[[查尔顿竞技足球俱乐部|查爾頓]]足球學校直到16歲。

2002年博伊德加盟[[英格蘭足球協會全國聯賽|足協全國聯賽]]球會[[保罗夫史提芬足球俱乐部|史提芬納治]]（Stevenage Borough），於12月14日主場對[[馬格特足球會|馬格特]]首次披甲上陣。2004年4月10日博伊德在作客[[諾夫維治維多利亞足球會|諾夫維治]]時取得首個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/3592677.stm |title=Northwich 1-2 Stevenage |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-04-10 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307021856/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/3592677.stm }}</ref></small>。2005/06年球季博伊德表現出色，到11月初已射入7球，並吸引數支[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]球隊的注意，史提芬納治隨即與他續約直到2008年<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stevenage/4428180.stm |title=Stevenage winger signs new deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-11-11 |accessdate=2009-04-27 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906052635/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stevenage/4428180.stm }}</ref></small>。2006年9月9日主場大勝[[斯塔福特流浪足球會|斯塔福特流浪]]6-0中大演[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/5308118.stm |title=Stevenage 6-0 Stafford Rangers |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-09-09 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906052744/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/5308118.stm }}</ref></small>。12月18日史提芬納治拒絕[[皮特堡联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]收購博伊德的出價<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stevenage/6189599.stm |title=Boro turn down Posh bid for Boyd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-12-18 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906052729/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/s/stevenage/6189599.stm }}</ref></small>。

在為史提芬納治出陣超過100場及射入25球後，博伊德於2007年1月8日正式加盟[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]]球會[[彼得伯勒联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]，其26萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]身價打破[[英格蘭足球協會全國聯賽|足協全國聯賽]]最高轉會費紀錄<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6221255.stm |title=Boyd finalises record Posh switch |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-08 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2017-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830020243/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6221255.stm }}</ref></small>。1月13日首次披甲在主場1-3不敵[[达灵顿足球俱乐部|達寧頓]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6236823.stm |title=Darlington 3-1 Peterborough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-13 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906052740/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6236823.stm }}</ref></small>，賽後領隊{{le|基夫·亞歷山大|Keith Alexander (footballer)|亞歷山大}}被辭退<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6264357.stm |title=Posh part company with Alexander |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-15 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2022-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220410005728/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6264357.stm }}</ref></small>，由[[达伦·弗格森|弗格森]]接任<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6282425.stm |title=Ferguson named Peterborough boss |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-20 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2020-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200513014119/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/6282425.stm }}</ref></small>。2月10日於主場3-0擊敗[[雷克斯汉姆足球俱乐部|域斯咸]]，博伊德射入加盟後首個入球，兼協助新領隊取得首場勝仗<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6327119.stm |title=Peterborough 3-0 Wrexham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-02-10 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906052559/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/6327119.stm }}</ref></small>。

[[2007年至2008年英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|2007/08年球季]]是博伊德效力彼德堡首個完整球季，他的表現出色，合共射入15球，包括在2008年1月15日主場8-2大破[[艾宁顿斯坦利足球俱乐部|阿克寧頓]]連中三元<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7184768.stm |title=Peterborough 8-2 Accrington |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-01-15 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2021-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327165950/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_3/7184768.stm }}</ref></small>，協助球隊奪得[[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|聯賽]]亞軍及自動升級[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]]席位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7357681.stm |title=Boss thrilled with Posh promotion |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-20 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310120154/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7357681.stm }}</ref></small>，更入選[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英格蘭足球乙級聯賽|英乙]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7370319.stm |title=Ronaldo named player of the year |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-04-27 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2019-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323131400/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/7370319.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。5月6日博伊德續簽四年新約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7386336.stm |title=Posh winger signs four-year deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-05-06 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307033811/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7386336.stm }}</ref></small>。

[[2008年至2009年英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|2008/09年球季]]博伊德狀態稍微回落，雖然上半季仍有7球斬獲，但部分彼德堡球迷對其不穩定的表現略有微言，但領隊戴倫·費格遜隨即挺身為護<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7839816.stm |title=Criticism not a problem for Boyd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-01-20 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310120221/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7839816.stm }}</ref></small>。下半季博伊德狀態回勇，在作客4-2擊敗[[布莱顿足球俱乐部|白禮頓]]後被戴倫·費格遜點名稱讚他是頂級球員<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7883077.stm |title=Ferguson dazzled by Boyd display |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-02-11 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307051804/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/7883077.stm }}</ref></small>。4月25日作客1-0擊敗[[科尔切斯特联足球俱乐部|高車士打]]後，彼德堡確保獲得[[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|聯賽]]亞軍，來季升級到[[英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|英冠]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8002029.stm |title=Peterborough win seals promotion |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-25 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2020-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030053450/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_2/8002029.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。4月26日博伊德入選[[英格蘭職業足球運動員協會|PFA]][[英格蘭足球甲級聯賽|英甲]][[PFA年度最佳陣容|年度最佳陣容]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8019726.stm |title=Giggs earns prestigious PFA award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-26 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2019-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190323131353/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/8019726.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年10月17日彼德堡作客對[[布里斯托尔城足球俱乐部|布里斯托城]]，博伊德在完場前頂入扳平1-1<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8302293.stm |title=Bristol City 1-1 Peterborough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-17 |accessdate=2009-10-20 |archive-date=2021-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211001204639/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8302293.stm }}</ref></small>，更以124場追平球會連續上陣最高紀錄<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8314084.stm |title=Boyd pleased to equal Posh record |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-10-19 |accessdate=2009-10-20 |archive-date=2018-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180906052607/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8314084.stm }}</ref></small>，翌週更連續上陣兩場打破紀錄<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/football/match_report/0,19764,11065_3149902,00.html |title=Boyd marks week to remember |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2009-10-24 |accessdate=2010-02-25}}</ref></small>，一直維持到2010年2月27日作客[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|史雲斯]]因患[[感冒|感冒]]缺陣才告終止，連續上陣場數達144場。

雖然彼德堡在[[英冠|英冠]]成績不振敬陪末席，博伊德仍然表現出色，以中場球員身份在上半季轟入12球，更被委任為[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]，於冬季轉會窗期間惹來多支球隊出價求購，但均被彼德堡一一回絕<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5915752,00.html |title=Posh shun deadline bids |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-03 |accessdate=2010-02-25 |archive-date=2010-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100208222155/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5915752,00.html }}</ref></small>，[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]是其中之一<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5977350,00.html |title=Posh confirm Boro interest |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-24 |accessdate=2010-02-25 |archive-date=2016-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308042121/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5977350,00.html }}</ref></small>。其後米杜士堡提出借用亦被拒絕，但仍有18個月合約在身的博伊德已確定不會續約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8534202.stm |title=Barry Fry expects George Boyd to stay at Peterborough |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-24 |accessdate=2010-02-26 |archive-date=2021-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210719103150/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/peterborough_united/8534202.stm }}</ref></small>。2010年3月2日博伊德被外借到[[英冠|英冠]]爭取升班球會[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]直到球季結束，更可於季後正式轉會<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8545062.stm |title=Nottingham Forest sign Peterborough's George Boyd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-03-02 |accessdate=2010-03-03 |archive-date=2010-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100307053845/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/nottm_forest/8545062.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。但博伊德在森林陣中苦苦掙扎，僅取得6場上陣機會，只在聯賽閉幕戰作客2-2賽和[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:斯坎索普; zh-hk:斯肯索普;}-]]射入一球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8646770.stm |title=Scunthorpe 2-2 Nottm Forest |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-05-02 |accessdate=2010-07-12 |archive-date=2021-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211001225704/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8646770.stm }}</ref></small>，在森林不成功的升班附加賽中沒有出賽，季後結束借用返回降班[[英甲|英甲]]的彼德堡。

2010年7月10日博伊德在對[[西汉姆联足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:西汉姆联; zh-hk:韋斯咸;}-]]的季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]前動筆簽署三年新約，結束不斷的離隊傳聞<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6254775,00.html |title=Posh secure Boyd's future |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-07-10 |accessdate=2010-07-12 |archive-date=2010-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100713111352/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,12875_6254775,00.html }}</ref></small>。

=== 國家隊 ===
博伊德在效力[[保罗夫史提芬足球俱乐部|史提芬納治]]（Stevenage Borough）時曾代表由23歲以下非[[英格蘭足球聯賽|聯賽]]球員組成的[[英格蘭足球代表丙隊|英格蘭C隊]]。2006年11月29日主場4-1擊敗荷蘭，博伊德射入首個國際賽入球，協助英格蘭贏得首屆[[歐洲挑戰錦標|歐洲挑戰錦標]]（European Challenge Trophy）<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/6158277.stm |title=England Nat Game XI 4-1 Holland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-11-29 |accessdate=2009-04-28 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310073800/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_conf/6158277.stm }}</ref></small>。

2009年4月，博伊德由於[[外祖父|外祖父]]在[[格拉斯哥|格拉斯哥]]出生而獲徵召加入[[蘇格蘭足球代表乙隊|蘇格蘭B隊]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8027973.stm |title=Posh's Boyd ready for Scots duty |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-04-30 |accessdate=2009-10-20 |archive-date=2017-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908202428/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8027973.stm }}</ref></small>，雖然曾惹來爭議<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8036587.stm |title=Gough queries Scots call for Boyd |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-06 |accessdate=2009-10-20 |archive-date=2021-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210512152633/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8036587.stm }}</ref></small>，但他仍於5月6日代表蘇格蘭B隊上陣出戰[[北愛爾蘭足球代表乙隊|北愛爾蘭B隊]]，並射入一球協助球隊以3-0獲勝<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/scotland/5287739/Andy-Webster-and-George-Boyd-give-Scotland-reasons-to-be-cheerful.html |title=Andy Webster and George Boyd give Scotland reasons to be cheerful |publisher=telegraph.co.uk |date=2009-05-06 |accessdate=2009-10-20 |archive-date=2009-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090511174826/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/international/scotland/5287739/Andy-Webster-and-George-Boyd-give-Scotland-reasons-to-be-cheerful.html }}</ref></small>。

